Mr. Blair C. PickerellChairman, Asia, Nikko Asset Management International Ltd.SingaporeIn his current role since 2010. He is recognized for his pioneering role in developing the Asian mutual funds business. Previously he was CEO Asia at Morgan Stanley Investment Management and held positions at a number of asset and investment management organizations in Hong Kong.2015 Annual ReportAdded to: Principal Financial Group Inc. - Des Moines, IAPrincipal is a financial products and services provider. Revenues are $12 billion.















 















 













Blair Pickerell to Head Morgan Stanley Investment Management in Asia
    

























































 






